{
  "texts": [
    "This seems especially true for perception-based RAI principles such as 'Transparency & Explainability' or 'Human Control' (versus more regulatory aspects such as 'Accountability').",
    "Such an approach is in line with the goal to create humancentred, ethical systems through fostering empathy-rather than promising a panacea.",
    "Practical example.",
    "The 'Unbias Fairness Toolkit' developed by Proboscis (Lane et al. 2018) foot_3 structures the dialogue with external stakeholders.",
    "The toolkit aims at stimulating public dialogue and engagement with the long-term goal of achieving a critical and collective approach to imagining the future of communities (Lane et al. 2018)."
  ]
}